PubMed is a popular website to query the research literature related to medicine and life science. PubMedÂ² is an experiment exploring new interactive ways to visualise the search results from PubMed on tablets, smart phones and classical computers.

How to use: Enter a normal PubMed or Google query, based on keywords. You can add the tag #review if you want to focus your search only on review articles.

Info:

Availability: www.pubmed-square.org
Author: www.samuelcroset.com
Source: https://github.com/loopasam/PubMedSquare
Bug report & feedback: http://www.samuelcroset.com/contact
Credit for JS lib: https://github.com/desandro/isotope
